<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko" xmlns:th="http://www.thymeleaf.org">
<head>
   <meta charset="utf-8" />
   <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
   <title>환영합니다 - Back-end API</title>
   <!-- Bootstrap CDN for simple styling -->
   <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-9ndCyUa6mY5Y5b3t+6bQZb1bZ6a2Q5Y1Zl3z9q+Y5u5l5e6V7m3Y8Jk9Q" crossorigin="anonymous">
   <style>
      body { padding-top: 3rem; }
      .hero { padding: 2rem; border-radius: .5rem; }
   </style>
</head>
<body class="bg-light">
   <div class="container">
      <header class="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center mb-4">
         <h2 class="m-0">Back-end API</h2>
         <nav>
            <a class="btn btn-outline-secondary btn-sm" href="/">홈</a>
         </nav>
      </header>

      <main>
         <div class="bg-white hero shadow-sm">
            <h1 class="display-6" th:text="${name} != null ? ${name} + '님, 환영합니다!' : '환영합니다!'">환영합니다!</h1>
            <p class="lead">간단한 환영 페이지입니다. API 문서나 UI로 이동하려면 위의 링크를 사용하세요.</p>
            <hr>
            <p>서버 시간: <strong th:text="${#dates.format(#dates.createNow(), 'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss')}">--:--:--</strong></p>
            <a class="btn btn-primary" href="/api">API 목록 보기</a>
         </div>
         <footer class="mt-4 text-muted small">&copy; 2026 Back-end API</footer>
      </main>
   </div>

   <!-- Optional: Bootstrap JS (not required for this simple page) -->
   <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" integrity="sha384-ENjdO4Dr2bkBIFxQpeoYz1HIcje39Wm4jDKdf19U8gI4ddQ3GYNS7NTKfAdVQSZe" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
</body>
</html>